{"tid":560464,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好鍾意屙頭啖屎","createTime":"2018-02-14T06:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T14:19:20.000Z","uid":31942,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e02d347a3b4b73ce5f238ec8108bd70daa8f41","tid":560464,"uid":31942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"入到去聞下空氣係咪清新<br />\n推開門 見到個白雪雪嘅屎坑 <br />\n望清楚個屎塔係咪乾淨<br />\n之後一野坐落去<br />\n凍冰冰 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屙屎個十幾分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反 有色嘅唔講<br />\n入到去有上手嘅味 香臭都好<br />\n又或者暖嘅<br />\n全部狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：屙緊頭啖屎"},{"pid":"6deeebf5f7167251e95096b5ddb684d015ed6d0c","tid":560464,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:50:30.000Z","msg":"都痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926ef1af438e8b4d91aa66546cf2ad8d1f91bf19","tid":560464,"uid":74207,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"接受吾到系出面屙屎"},{"pid":"16ea3be3ea7faffc4b2ce3ab85f73d4d91da0db7","tid":560464,"uid":36702,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"我每屙完一次屎都搵師傅換個新馬桶"},{"pid":"810c72cdb9f2222a476ac2299fde59560fcd17cf","tid":560464,"uid":128325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:55:53.000Z","msg":"第一個屙屎都可以打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7580381f00d3700fa83e40175c18406cf2ce4daf","tid":560464,"uid":123103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T06:57:40.000Z","msg":"公司廁所好乾淨就會。。"},{"pid":"d05c0064987f505e09c417c8529c3904c4e78a2e","tid":560464,"uid":123456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"